trans-unit.source: Specifies information about how a document is printed, including the printer that prints it, when printing from a Windows Forms application.
trans-unit.target: Anger information om hur ett dokument skrivs ut, inklusive skrivare som skriver ut det, när du skriver ut från en Windows Forms-program.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you access a PrinterSettings through <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrinterSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties to modify printer settings.
trans-unit.target: Normalt kommer du till ett PrinterSettings via <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrinterSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName>eller <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Egenskaper för att ändra skrivarinställningar.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrinterSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The most common printer setting is <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterName%2A>, which specifies the printer to print to.
trans-unit.target: De vanligaste skrivarinställningen är <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterName%2A>, vilket innebär att skriva ut till skrivaren.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterName%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about printing with Windows Forms, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: Mer information om utskrifter med Windows Forms finns i <xref:System.Drawing.Printing>namnområde Översikt.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: If you wish to print from a Windows Presentation Foundation application, see the <xref:System.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill skriva ut från ett Windows Presentation Foundation-program finns i <xref:System.Printing>namnområde.</xref:System.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes all fields to their default values.
trans-unit.target: Standardkonstruktorn initierar alla fält till respektive standardvärde.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you do not create an instance of <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings>, but instead use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrinterSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to set settings for the printer.
trans-unit.target: Normalt du inte skapar en instans av <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings>, utan i stället används den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrinterSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName>att ange inställningar för skrivare.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrinterSettings%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the printer supports double-sided printing.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om skrivaren stöder dubbelsidig utskrift.

trans-unit.source: To print using duplex, and if the printer supports it, set <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.Duplex%2A> to one of the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.Duplex> values.
trans-unit.target: Med hjälp av duplex och om skrivaren stöder det. Ange <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.Duplex%2A>till en av de <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.Duplex>värden.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.Duplex> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.Duplex%2A>

trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om skrivaren som stöder dubbelsidig utskrift Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: En kopia av det här objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the printed document is collated.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger om utskriften är sorterad.

trans-unit.source: Collating is performed only when the number of copies is greater than 1.
trans-unit.target: Sortera utförs endast när antalet kopior som är större än 1.

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.Copies%2A> property to specify the number of copies to print.
trans-unit.target: Ange <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.Copies%2A>egenskapen för att ange hur många kopior som ska skriva ut.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.Copies%2A>

trans-unit.source: Setting Collate to `true` will print a complete copy of the document before the first page of the next copy is printed.
trans-unit.target: Ange sortera till `true` skrivs ut en fullständig kopia av dokumentet innan den första sidan i nästa kopia skrivs ut.

trans-unit.source: `false` will print each page by the number of copies specified before printing the next page.
trans-unit.target: `false`varje sida skrivs ut av antal kopior innan du skriver ut nästa sida.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the printed document is collated; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om utskriften är sorterad; Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of copies of the document to print.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger antal kopior av dokumentet skrivs ut.

trans-unit.source: Not all printers support printing multiple copes.
trans-unit.target: Alla skrivare stöder inte skriva ut flera copes.

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.MaximumCopies%2A> property to determine the maximum number of copies the printer supports.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.MaximumCopies%2A>egenskapen fastställa det maximala antalet kopierar skrivare stöder.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.MaximumCopies%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the number of copies is set higher than the maximum copies supported by the printer, only the maximum number of copies will be printed, and no exception will occur.
trans-unit.target: Om antalet kopior är högre än de maximala kopior som stöds av skrivaren, bara det maximala antalet kopior som ska skrivas ut och inget undantag inträffar.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Some printers might not support printing more than one copy at a time.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Vissa skrivare stöder inte skriva ut mer än en kopia i taget.

trans-unit.source: The number of copies to print.
trans-unit.target: Antalet kopior som ska skrivas ut.

trans-unit.source: The default is 1.
trans-unit.target: Standard är 1.

trans-unit.source: The value of the Copies property is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för kopior egenskapen är mindre än noll.

trans-unit.source: Gets the default page settings for this printer.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar standard inställningar för den här skrivaren.

trans-unit.source: Page settings include the size of the margins on the page, the size of paper to use, and whether to print in color.
trans-unit.target: Inställningarna omfattar storleken på marginaler på sidan, storleken på papper som ska användas och om du vill skriva ut i färg.

trans-unit.source: For more information about page settings, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings> class.
trans-unit.target: Mer information om inställningar finns i <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>klass.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings"></xref> that represents the default page settings for this printer.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings"> </xref> som representerar till standardinställningarna för den här skrivaren.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the printer setting for double-sided printing.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger skrivarinställningen för dubbelsidig utskrift.

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.CanDuplex%2A> property to check to see if the printer supports duplex printing.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.CanDuplex%2A>egenskapen för att kontrollera om skrivaren stöder dubbelsidig utskrift.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.CanDuplex%2A>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.Duplex"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: En av de <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.Duplex"> </xref> värden.

trans-unit.source: The default is determined by the printer.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet bestäms av skrivaren.

trans-unit.source: The value of the Duplex property is not one of the <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.Duplex"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Värdet på egenskapen Duplex är inte en av de <xref href="System.Drawing.Printing.Duplex"> </xref> värden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the page number of the first page to print.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger sidnumret på första sidan för att skriva ut.

trans-unit.source: The FromPage and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A> properties are used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog> when the user selects a print range.
trans-unit.target: FromPage och <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A>Egenskaper som används av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>när användaren väljer ett print intervall.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSomePages%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property must be set to `true` to enable the user to specify a print range.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSomePages%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen måste anges till `true` så att användare ska ange ett intervall för utskrift.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSomePages%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In addition, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog> requires the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.MinimumPage%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.MaximumPage%2A> to be specified and the FromPage value to be within that range.
trans-unit.target: Dessutom den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>kräver den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.MinimumPage%2A>och <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.MaximumPage%2A>anges och värdet ska ligga inom intervallet FromPage.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.MaximumPage%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.MinimumPage%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>

trans-unit.source: During the printing process, in the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName> event, view the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A> to determine what should be printed.
trans-unit.target: Under processen för utskrift, i den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName>händelse, visa den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A>att avgöra vad som ska skrivas.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A> is <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName>, use the FromPage and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A> properties to determine what pages should be printed.
trans-unit.target: Om <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A>är <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName>, använda på FromPage och <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A>Egenskaper för att avgöra vilka sidor som ska skrivas.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A> is <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName>, then specify output only for the selected pages.
trans-unit.target: Om <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A>är <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName>, ange utdata endast för de valda sidorna.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A>

trans-unit.source: The FromPage, <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A> can also be set programmatically, though the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName> implementation is the same.
trans-unit.target: FromPage, <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A>och <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A>kan också anges programmässigt, men den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName>implementering är samma.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrintRange%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A>

trans-unit.target: Sidnumret på första sidan för att skriva ut.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the page numbers that the user has specified to be printed.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger nummer som användaren har angett ska skrivas ut.

trans-unit.source: The PrintRange property is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>.when the user selects a print range.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen PrintRange används av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>. när användaren markerar ett print område.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>

trans-unit.source: The default PrintRange is `AllPages`.
trans-unit.target: Standardvärdet är PrintRange `AllPages`.

trans-unit.source: To enable the user to specify a range of pages to print, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSomePages%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property must be set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Så här aktiverar du att användaren anger ett sidintervall som ska skrivas ut, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSomePages%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen måste anges till `true`.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSomePages%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To enable the user to specify the selected pages to print, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSelection%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property must be set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Att aktivera användaren att ange de valda sidorna som ska skrivas ut, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSelection%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen måste anges till `true`.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowSelection%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: During the printing process, in the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName> event, view the PrintRange to determine what should be printed.
trans-unit.target: Under processen för utskrift, i den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName>händelse, visa PrintRange avgör vad som ska skrivas.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If PrintRange is <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName>, use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.FromPage%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A> properties to determine what pages should be printed.
trans-unit.target: Om PrintRange är <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName>, använda på <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.FromPage%2A>och <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A>Egenskaper för att avgöra vilka sidor som ska skrivas.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.FromPage%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If PrintRange is <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName>, then specify output only for the selected pages.
trans-unit.target: Om PrintRange är <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName>, ange utdata endast för de valda sidorna.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintRange?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.FromPage%2A>, <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A> and PrintRange can also be set programmatically, though the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName> implementation is the same.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.FromPage%2A>, <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A>och PrintRange kan också anges programmässigt, men den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName>implementering är samma.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.PrintPage?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.ToPage%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.FromPage%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the printing output is sent to a file instead of a port.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett värde som anger om utskrift utdata skickas till en fil i stället för en port.

trans-unit.source: The PrintToFile property is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog> when the user selects the **Print to file** option.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen PrintToFile används av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>när användaren väljer den **Skriv till fil** alternativet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>

trans-unit.source: In such a case, the output port is set to "FILE," causing the Windows printing subsystem to prompt the user for a file name when the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method is called.
trans-unit.target: I sådana fall på utdataporten anges till "Fil" orsakar undersystemet Windows utskrift att uppmana användaren att ange en fil när den <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden anropas.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The PrintToFile property is only used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog> and cannot be set programmatically.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > I PrintToFile egenskapen används endast av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>och kan inte anges via programmering.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>

trans-unit.source: The `Print to file` option only appears on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog> when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowPrintToFile%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Den `Print to file` alternativet visas bara på den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>när den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowPrintToFile%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskap är inställd på `true`.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog.AllowPrintToFile%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog>
